# Input

```scss
.example {
  $local-var:   10px;
  ns.$namespaced-var:    20px;
  $default-var:   red   !default;
  $global-var:blue!global;
  $combined:green!global!default!global;

  padding:   $local-var;
  margin:  ns.$namespaced-var;
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
.example {
	$local-var: 10px;
	ns.$namespaced-var: 20px;
	$default-var: red !default;
	$global-var: blue !global;
	$combined: green !default !global !global;

	padding: $local-var;
	margin: ns.$namespaced-var;
}

```
